text: Barbara (n√©e Barry) Gronemus (November 21, 1931 - January 17, 2021) was an American politician and farmer. Gronemus was born in Norwalk, Wisconsin. She was a Democratic Party member of the Wisconsin State Assembly from 1982 through 2008. Gronemus died in Blair, Wisconsin on January 17, 2021 at the age of 89.'Wisconsin Blue Book 2007-2008,' Biographical Sketch of Barbara Gronemus, pg. 81Barbara "Bobby" Gronemus|1931-2021|Obituary ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2021 deaths Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from Wisconsin Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
